OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779534180
OL,3,CMichael Carrick signs two year
OL,4,Ccontract as Manchester United Head
OL,5,CCoach
OL,7,FManchester United have finally
OL,8,Fconfirmed Michael Carrick is staying
OL,9,Fas head coach after agreeing a deal
OL,10,Funtil 2028.
OL,12,FThe former Red Devils midfielder,
OL,13,Fcaptain and coach has improved results
OL,14,Fand morale since being brought in for
OL,15,Fthe remainder of the campaign
OL,16,Ffollowing Ruben Amorim's acrimonious
OL,17,FJanuary exit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
