PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779534180
OL,3,CMichael Carrick signs two year
OL,4,Ccontract as Manchester United Head
OL,5,CCoach
OL,7,FCarrick has won 11 of 16 games since
OL,8,Ftaking charge, guiding United to a
OL,9,Fthird place finish, and Champions
OL,10,FLeague football next season.
OL,12,FSpeaking to the club's in-house media,
OL,13,FUnited's Head Coach said: "From the
OL,14,Fmoment that I arrived here 20 years
OL,15,Fago, I felt the magic of Manchester
OL,16,FUnited.
OL,18,F"Carrying the responsibility of
OL,19,Fleading our special football club
OL,20,Ffills me with immense pride.
OL,26,@uD@[OUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
