PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779534180
OL,3,CMichael Carrick signs two year
OL,4,Ccontract as Manchester United Head
OL,5,CCoach
OL,7,F"Throughout the past five months, this
OL,8,Fgroup of players have shown they can
OL,9,Freach the standards of resilience,
OL,10,Ftogetherness and determination that we
OL,11,Fdemand here.
OL,13,F"Now it's time to move forward
OL,14,Ftogether again, with ambition and a
OL,15,Fclear sense of purpose. Manchester
OL,16,FUnited and our incredible supporters
OL,17,Fdeserve to be challenging for the
OL,18,Fbiggest honours again."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
