PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779534180
OL,3,CMichael Carrick signs two year
OL,4,Ccontract as Manchester United Head
OL,5,CCoach
OL,7,FJason Wilcox, Manchester United
OL,8,FDirector of Football, said: "Michael
OL,9,Fhas thoroughly earned the opportunity
OL,10,Fto continue leading our men's team. In
OL,11,Fthe time he has been doing the role,
OL,12,Fwe have seen positive results on the
OL,13,Fpitch, but more than that, an approach
OL,14,Fwhich aligns with the club's values,
OL,15,Ftraditions and history.
OL,26,@pD@]OU
