PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779534180
OL,3,CMichael Carrick signs two year
OL,4,Ccontract as Manchester United Head
OL,5,CCoach
OL,7,F"Michael's achievements in leading the
OL,8,Fclub back to the Champions League
OL,9,Fshould not be understated. He has
OL,10,Fforged a strong bond with the players
OL,11,Fand can be proud of the winning
OL,12,Fculture at Carrington and in the
OL,13,Fdressing room, which we are continuing
OL,14,Fto build."
OL,16,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,17,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,18,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,19,Four region.
